{"tid":1224213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急/請廣傳] 政府暫緩以退為進，星期日香港人唔出嚟將會一敗塗地！","createTime":"2019-06-15T02:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T00:35:28.000Z","uid":36592,"like":610,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":117,"replies":[{"pid":"2097d0599de4f59d24880a90476aee1418f67dda","tid":1224213,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"經過69百萬人遊行同612血腥鎮壓，政府既管治合法性已經危在旦夕，全世界都等緊機會作致命一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家政府扮聽民意暫緩修例，目的係以退為進，買時間令善忘既香港人沖淡怒氣，同時令國際社會無機會出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果香港人因為政府暫緩而星期日唔出嚟，之後將會係連場既大規模清算同白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到時候無人會再敢抗爭，惡法原封不動通過，69既百萬人遊行，612義士既犧牲將會毀於一旦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你唔想呢件事發生，就要趁全世界站係香港人一方，民氣最強既時候出黎遊行，堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢場仗冇階段性勝利，一係贏，一係輸，winner takes all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港要贏，香港人星期日一定要出嚟，多你一個絕對好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊記目標只有一個：撤回惡法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家copy呢個post喺Facebook, IG, Whatsapp share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣組幫手整圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用盡你一切方法動員認識既人星期日出嚟堅持撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58f85000b1b6dba9a3330a97ec599585539eaa1b","tid":1224213,"uid":137088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T02:38:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c2441031d6c47da00a4a386e84c713742127f4","tid":1224213,"uid":36592,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedB